# About

Pablo Murad is a Brazilian entrepreneur building scalable projects across technology, education, and construction. His work focuses on democratizing knowledge and creating accessible solutions that expand opportunity in Brazil and beyond. He's also a longtime transhumanism enthusiast, exploring how technology can push human potential forward.

The Great Capsule of Pablo Murad is a personal space for exploration and an informal archive: reading trails, mirrored and curated texts, letters, and links. It exists as a single place to wander, discover, and follow threads without the noise of the open web.
---

By Pablo Murad — 2024–2026
